-	Prompt Customer to enter name
-	Get name
-	Prompt customer to enter Customer Number
-	Get Customer number
-	Prompt customer to enter sales amount
-	Get Sales amount
-	Prompt customer to enter tax code
-	Get Tax code
-	If tax code is =0, set sales tax =0
-	If tax code =1, set sales tax = sales amount*0.02
-	If tax code=2, set sales tax = sales amount *0.05
-	Calculate Total amount due by adding sales amount and sales tax
-	Print out a sales report
-	Print out Customer number
-	Print out Customer name
-	Print out sales amount
-	Print out sales tax
-	Print out total amount due
